      assess: 'Confirmed third-party signal is thin this window — one exploited vendor tool. We assess with low confidence that malicious packages aimed at payment applications on public code registries are the growth edge; several reports point that way, but each awaits corroboration.', assessSup: '1', conf: 'low confidence',
